3 Sec. 2. “Agrivoltaic purposes” means a system:
4 1. Under which solar energy production and agricultural use occurs in an
5 integrated manner on the same piece of land; and
6 2. Which incorporates designs, technologies or configurations conducive to
7 integrating agricultural activities with solar energy production on the same piece
8 of land.
